Sentencas: PrSr3Fe3-yNiyO10-gamma (PSFNO10, 0 < y < 0.2) was synthesized and investigated for the potential active cathode of a solid oxide fuel cell operating at low temperature.
Titulo: Ni doped PrSr3Fe3O10-δ Ruddlesden-Popper oxide for active oxygen reduction cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Effects of Ni substitution in PrSr3Fe3O10 on the structure, thermal expansion property, electrical conductivity, and cathodic performance of SOFC were studied.
Titulo: Ni doped PrSr3Fe3O10-δ Ruddlesden-Popper oxide for active oxygen reduction cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: PSFNO10 has a tetragonal crystal structure with a I4/mmm space group.
Titulo: Ni doped PrSr3Fe3O10-δ Ruddlesden-Popper oxide for active oxygen reduction cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The unit cell parameter and crystallite size decreased when Ni was substituted at the Fe site.
Titulo: Ni doped PrSr3Fe3O10-δ Ruddlesden-Popper oxide for active oxygen reduction cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: However, the electrical conductivity of PSFO10 was hardly changed by the addition of Ni and the dominant hole conduction was observed in PSFNO10 with and without Ni doping.
Titulo: Ni doped PrSr3Fe3O10-δ Ruddlesden-Popper oxide for active oxygen reduction cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The thermal expansion coefficient (TEC) was decreased by addition of Ni and the TEC was in good agreement with that of LSGM electrolyte.
Titulo: Ni doped PrSr3Fe3O10-δ Ruddlesden-Popper oxide for active oxygen reduction cathode for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The power density of the single planar cell using PSFNO10 (Ni = 10 mol%) cathode achieved the large power density of 679 mW/cm(2) and the cathodic overpotential was 131.3 mV at 1.25 A cm(-2) at 1073 K. (C) 2016
Titulo: Ni doped PrSr3Fe3O10-δ Ruddlesden-Popper oxide for active oxygen reduction cathode for solid oxide fuel cell
